<HEADLINE>  Dutch Journalist Killed in E. Timor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DILI, East Timor (AP) -- As international peacekeepers worked to  
restore order to East Timor, a Dutch journalist was killed and two 
other Western reporters escaped an armed attack without injury. 
</P>
<P>
	The attackers in both incidents remained unidentified Wednesday,  
although they appeared to be linked to pro-Indonesian militias that 
