	Sept. 28: Actress Brigitte Bardot is 65. Director-actor John  
Sayles is 49. Actress Sylvia Kristel (``Emmanuelle'') is 47. 
Actress Janeane Garofalo is 35. TV personality Moon Zappa is 32. 
</P>
<P>
	Sept. 29: Actress Anita Ekberg is 68. Singer Jerry Lee Lewis is  
64. Actor Larry Linville (``M.A.S.H.'') is 60. Actress Madeline 
Kahn is 57. Musician Mike Pinera of Iron Butterfly is 51. TV 
personality Bryant Gumbel is 51. Comedian-actor Andrew ``Dice'' 
