<HEADLINE> Courtney Cox Marries David Arquette </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- She is the actress formerly known as Courtney  
Cox. 
</P>
<P>
	The ``Friends'' star, who wed actor David Arquette on June 12,  
has officially changed her name to Courtney Cox Arquette. 
</P>
<P>
	``It's for real. It's on my Social Security card, everything. No  
